name: ULTMMA Staff T-Shirt
description:
Be part of the team and support your local MMA scene with the ULTMMA staff T-Shirt. The front features our classic Tiger unleashing a left high kick ULTMMA logo design along with the website’s URL below. On the back the phrase “Support Local MMA” is written in a bold font. 

The Shirt is 100% ring spun cotton 30/1's fine knit jersey, tubular construction, ribbed crew taped neck and shoulders with double needle sleeves and bottom hem. Includes Tear-Away tag

name: American Pride T-Shirt
description:
ULTMMA American Pride T-Shirt features a rising American Bald Eagle spreading its wings in a red burst of color over the ULTMMA logo. Above the eagle is a single white star. The whole shirt design comes on a rich navy blue T-Shirt. On the upper back of the shirt is the American flag with the statement "Support Local MMA" written below.   


*Flat & same day shipping on this order* 


The Shirt is 100% ring spun cotton 30/1's fine knit jersey, tubular construction, ribbed crew taped neck and shoulders with double needle sleeves and bottom hem. Includes Tear-Away tag

name: Vintage T-Shirt
description:
ULTMMA Vintage T-Shirt takes a classic interpretation on the local MMA scene. Going back to a time when supporting local MMA wasn’t the cool thing to do, this design features a US shield flanked by gray and white stars. 

The center is held together by an old school banner that reads “ULTMMA” with the phrase “Support Local MMA” written below. The color is a white shirt with gray and white designs. 

*Flat & same day shipping on this order*

The Shirt is 100% ring spun cotton 30/1's fine knit jersey, tubular construction, ribbed crew taped neck and shoulders with double needle sleeves and bottom hem. Includes Tear-Away tag
